@startuml
actor User
participant "Web Client (React)" as FE
participant "API Server" as API
participant "Application Layer" as APP
database "Database" as DB

User -> FE: Start Scenario
FE -> API: GET /api/scenario/{id}
API -> APP: Fetch scenario data
APP -> DB: Query questions + answers
DB --> APP: Return results
APP --> API: Return scenario model
API --> FE: JSON Response (Questions)

User -> FE: Selects answer
FE -> API: POST /api/response
API -> APP: Handle CreateResponse
APP -> DB: Insert Response
DB --> APP: Success
APP --> API: Result
API --> FE: Acknowledgement

@enduml
